query: SELECT queryid ,query, local_blks_read, total_time, rows,userid,temp_blks_read, $1 * shared_blks_hit / nullif(shared_blks_hit + shared_blks_read, $2) AS hit_percen FROM pg_stat_statements ORDER BY total_time DESC LIMIT $3
SELECT queryid,query, calls, total_time, rows, $1 * shared_blks_hit / nullif(shared_blks_hit + shared_blks_read, $2) AS hit_percen FROM pg_stat_statements ORDER BY total_time DESC LIMIT $3

/*pga4dash*/
SELECT
   (SELECT sum(blks_read) FROM pg_stat_database WHERE datname = (SELECT datname FROM pg_database WHERE oid = $1)) AS "Reads",
   (SELECT sum(blks_hit) FROM pg_stat_database WHERE datname = (SELECT datname FROM pg_database WHERE oid = $2)) AS "Hits"

/*pga4dash*/
SELECT
   (SELECT sum(tup_inserted) FROM pg_stat_database WHERE datname = (SELECT datname FROM pg_database WHERE oid = $1)) AS "Inserts",
   (SELECT sum(tup_updated) FROM pg_stat_database WHERE datname = (SELECT datname FROM pg_database WHERE oid = $2)) AS "Updates",
   (SELECT sum(tup_deleted) FROM pg_stat_database WHERE datname = (SELECT datname FROM pg_database WHERE oid = $3)) AS "Deletes"

/*pga4dash*/
SELECT
   (SELECT sum(tup_fetched) FROM pg_stat_database WHERE datname = (SELECT datname FROM pg_database WHERE oid = $1)) AS "Fetched",
   (SELECT sum(tup_returned) FROM pg_stat_database WHERE datname = (SELECT datname FROM pg_database WHERE oid = $2)) AS "Returned"

/*pga4dash*/
SELECT
   (SELECT sum(xact_commit) + sum(xact_rollback) FROM pg_stat_database WHERE datname = (SELECT datname FROM pg_database WHERE oid = $1)) AS "Transactions",
   (SELECT sum(xact_commit) FROM pg_stat_database WHERE datname = (SELECT datname FROM pg_database WHERE oid = $2)) AS "Commits",
   (SELECT sum(xact_rollback) FROM pg_stat_database WHERE datname = (SELECT datname FROM pg_database WHERE oid = $3)) AS "Rollbacks"

/*pga4dash*/
SELECT
   (SELECT count(*) FROM pg_stat_activity WHERE datname = (SELECT datname FROM pg_database WHERE oid = $1)) AS "Total",
   (SELECT count(*) FROM pg_stat_activity WHERE state = $2 AND datname = (SELECT datname FROM pg_database WHERE oid = $3))  AS "Active",
   (SELECT count(*) FROM pg_stat_activity WHERE state = $4 AND datname = (SELECT datname FROM pg_database WHERE oid = $5))  AS "Idle"
